				<wikidot:authorName>A Random Day</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1841781</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I recognize that you’re constrained to a large extent by your containment procedures. However, I’ve long since become jaded to collapsibles that hide The True SCP Article. If possible, I would have framed the article around the Mind over Metaphysics book — making it Thaumiel — and the collapsible would have simply revealed that none of its effects should actually work.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
